title: Lotte
description: Health food chain with stores in the U.S. Sells food from Korea, South Asia, Latin America and India. The Indian isle has the most vegan food. In the back of the produce section is bulk tofu which is $3.95 for six pounds and $4.95 for 6 pounds of firm tofu. Also in that section is smaller tofu and tofu products at reasonable prices. Carries produce, soy milk, teas and more.
